 Leon has been hard at work building his structure for this years Garden Festival in Singapore. Lowvelder had previously reported on his progress and are happy to announce he is indeed the best in the world. Leon received a gold medal as well as ‘Best Horticultural use in landscape’ in the entire 11 day festival. On top of that Leon’s installation “African Thunder” won Best on show of the entire Garden festival. Also read: Leon Kluge hard at work preparing for the Singapore Garden Festival 2018 Although Leon is making great strides as an international landscape architect, the Lowveld’s Leon Kluge has not forgotten his South African roots. #SingaporeGardenfestival   (function(d, s, id) {  var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];  if (d.getElementById(id)) return;  js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;  js.src = 'https://connect.facebook.net/en_GB/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v3.0';  fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);}(document, 'script', 'facebook-jssdk')); 